Package com.jme.util

Class LittleEndien

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • com.jme.util.LittleEndien
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.DataInput, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class LittleEndien
extends java.io.InputStream
implements java.io.DataInput
    LittleEndien is a class to read little-endian stored data via a InputStream. All functions work as defined in DataInput, but assume they come from a LittleEndien input stream. Currently used to read .ms3d and .3ds files.
    Author:
    Jack Lindamood
